<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ʿạly wʿạly wʿlynạk .. ạ̹ḥnạ wlạdk ʿd ʿynạk
 yạ rbnạ ntmny̱ rḍạk .. yswʿnạ ạlgẖạly mạ ạ̉ḥlạk
 1- (mlk ạlkwn bkl zmạn .. wbạ̹ydk kl ạlslṭạn)2
 tạ̉mr tnhy ʿ ạlạ̹nsạn .. ạldfẗ bạ̹ydk yạ qbṭạn
 2- (ạ̉nạ wkẖwty tkẖlynạ .. bkẓẗ ạ̹ydk tḥmynạ)2
 nṭq ạ̹blys wnḍwjh .. wmạ yqdr yfk ḥlqh
 3- (nṣly hkdẖ wnqlk .. yạ rạʿy bạrk sẖʿbk)2
 ạgẖsẖʿnạ ṭybẗ qlbk .. ạsẖqd ḥlwẗ ʿsẖrtk</lyrics>
<title>ʿạly wʿạly</title>
